{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01QT8htTrAEjwhHFn2Xrm1iU","type":"tool_result","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Here is the summary:\n\n**PM2 Processes -- All online.** No processes are down. Two have elevated restart counts:\n- `pezant-tools`: 13 restarts -- flagged as high but consistent with previous fix-checker runs (was 13 in runs 80-82 as well, so no new restarts; normal drift).\n- `claude-bot`: 43 restarts -- same count as runs 80-82, no new restarts; normal drift for a long-running bot process.\n- All three staging services (`runeval-staging`, `promptlibrary-staging`, `grocerygenius-staging`) are online with low restart counts (2-4).\n\n**Autonomous Dev Progress Log -- Healthy.** Runs 42-45 all completed cleanly. The latest work (Run 45) was a comprehensive WCAG accessibility pass on runeval, deployed to staging successfully. No FAIL entries found.\n\n**Fix-Checker Failure Log -- Healthy.** Runs 80-82 all report clean results. Run 82 did a minor cleanup (deleted a stale branch in runeval) but no actual failures. 501 tests passing across all repos, all builds clean, no open PRs, no stuck branches.\n\n**All clear.**"},{"type":"text","text":"agentId: a9994c766c2529f98 (use SendMessage with to: 'a9994c766c2529f98' to continue this agent)\n<usage>total_tokens: 13761\ntool_uses: 5\nduration_ms: 28529</usage>"}]}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"f64a6d3f-4690-4a87-aa5b-66418f809ed2","uuid":"5add613c-4e8b-4c31-be73-66648510309a","timestamp":"2026-03-20T13:21:04.278Z","tool_use_result":{"status":"completed","prompt":"You are a fix-checker agent. Check staging services and recent autonomous dev logs.\n\n1. Check PM2 processes on the VM:\n```bash\nssh REDACTED_VM_HOST \"pm2 jlist\" 2>/dev/null\n```\nLook for processes with status !== \"online\" or high restart counts (>10). Report any staging processes that are down.\n\n2. Read the autonomous dev progress log:\n```bash\ncat REDACTED_REPOS_ROOT/auto-dev/logs/progress.md